-- NRB Bearings Raises Third-Quarter Sales Growth Forecast to 20%, CEO Says
-- B y   R u c h i k a   T u l s h y a n
-- 2010-10-14T06:39:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-14/nrb-bearings-raises-third-quarter-sales-growth-forecast-to-20-ceo-says.html
NRB Bearings Ltd. raised its third-
quarter sales growth forecast to 20 percent from 15 percent,
Managing Director Harshbeena Sahney Zaveri said in an interview
with Bloomberg UTV today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
